  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="FR">Think Climate Indonesia : co&#xFB;ts d&#x2019;exploitation</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Think Climate Indonesia: Operating costs</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="FR">Ce projet appuiera la mise en &#x153;uvre du programme Think Climate Indonesia &#x2013; un programme de renforcement organisationnel et de recherche de base &#x2013; en couvrant ses co&#xFB;ts d&#x2019;exploitation. Des approbations distinctes autoriseront l&#x2019;ex&#xE9;cution de projets et d&#x2019;activit&#xE9;s individuels touchant la gouvernance, la communication et l&#x2019;&#xE9;valuation des programmes.

Le programme Think Climate Indonesia est un partenariat entre le CRDI et Oak Foundation. Il s&#x2019;agit d&#x2019;un investissement conjoint de 2 520 000 CAD sur 36 mois dont le but est d&#x2019;aider l&#x2019;Indon&#xE9;sie &#xE0; faire des progr&#xE8;s relativement &#xE0; la r&#xE9;alisation de ses engagements en mati&#xE8;re d&#x2019;att&#xE9;nuation des changements climatiques et &#xE0; participer efficacement aux mesures d&#x2019;adaptation aux changements climatiques. Le CRDI sera responsable du suivi, de la surveillance des programmes et du soutien des capacit&#xE9;s pour les partenaires.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will support the implementation of the Think Climate Indonesia &#x2013; Organizational Strengthening and Core Research Program by covering operational costs. Separate approvals will authorize the execution of individual projects and activities related to program governance, communication, and evaluation.

The Think Climate Indonesia program is a partnership between IDRC and the Oak Foundation. It represents a joint investment of CA$2,520,000 over 36 months aimed at supporting Indonesia in making progress toward its climate mitigation commitments and effectively engaging in climate adaptation actions. IDRC will be responsible for program oversight, capacity support to partners, and monitoring.</narrative>
  </description>
